name: Froggy Jumper
description:
/!\ An first-year video game school project (2 weeks in e-art sup Strasbourg) at the start of the year, discovering Unity tools. /!\

`` You are a frog who needs to reach the end of each levels. The three levels are unique in their own ways, but when you find ennemies, to eliminate them, you have to jump at them. Be sure to kill all ennemies of a level to reach the end. ``

All credits goes for all the assets goes to their authors in the Unity asset store.
